<li>B站UP主：草帽sMao：<a href="https://space.bilibili.com/108104104?spm_id_from=333.788.b_765f7570696e666f.2">https://space.bilibili.com/108104104?spm_id_from=333.788.b_765f7570696e666f.2</a></li>
<li>官网教程（需要科学）<a href="https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCQsVmhSa4X-G3lHlUtejzLA/featured">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCQsVmhSa4X-G3lHlUtejzLA/featured</a></li>
